Development Installation:
=========================

-download xataface zip file
-extract in a directory
-copy application directory files from a full installation on oxywn, e.g. conf.ini, tables/, template_c
-note: template_c files can be deleted whenever, they are auto-created

-requires PHP and MySQL

## Xataface Php7.2 Mysqli on Ubuntu (PHP >5 requires Mysqli!)
## Php7 has built-in server for development

sudo apt install php-7.2 php-7.2-mysql

##then start built-in server in the application directory
php -S localhost:8085 -t /home/dorothea/Programming/xatasstemdb

(!configure driver=mysqli in conf.ini of xatasstemdb!)

